						               													<description>The object of the game is to go out and by landing directly on one of many slightly shady establishments on the board, score one kilo of stash. In case you have forgotten, that is 35 lids. Should you go to jail you lose all of the lids you are carrying that are not safe. You lose 2 turns but can go free by rolling doubles on either throw or by paying $50 immediately.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You may go out and return home as many times as pessary, each time you return home you get an additional $75.00 and all the lids you are carrying are Safe. You may attempt to score your kilo in one trip around the board and return home, winning the game. But remember, anyone landing on the same space as you may take one of your lids you are carrying.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After landing directly on the scoring place, the price of your lids is determined by retooling the dice and paying the number rolled for each lid. You may purchase all or part of the number of lids listed for that scoring establishment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
